"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-01-olympic-ball-girl-goes-viral-giving-novak-djokovic-a-flirty-look-21346148\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"An Olympic tennis ball girl has gone viral for givingNovak Djokovica flirty look during his 6-3 7-6 (7-3) win over Stefanos Tsitsipas inParison Thursday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic is likely making his last Olympic appearance and is keen to land a gold medal, given it's one of the only things missing from the GOAT's trophy cabinet.\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999994565769, \"rank\": 5.435245744618622e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"score\": 0.7168567345960191, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GOAT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old's victory over Tsitsipas means Djokovic has become the oldest player in history to reach the semi-finals of the Olympic singles tournament.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999994565769, \"rank\": 5.435245744618622e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is now guaranteed a spot in a medal match - which will be for the gold or silver if he wins in the last four - or for the bronze if he loses to Lorenzo Musetti.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 622, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorenzo Musetti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic, though, picked up a nasty-looking knee injury during his triumph over Tsitsipas and there are genuine fears he could withdraw ahead of the semi-finals.\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-time Grand Slam champion is adamant he will do everything he can to play through the knee problem and keep his hopes of landing a medal alive.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even if the doctor says the knee is not ok, I will probably get on the court and give it a try,' Djokovic said after the match.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999994565769, \"rank\": 5.435245744618622e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'These are very rare chances to fight for a medal for my country, so I am going to do everything possible in the next 24 hours to put myself in a position to fight for a medal for Serbia.'\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.8899335952631143, \"rank\": 0.12357426552475226, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, an incident during the Djokovic-Tsitsipas clash at Roland-Garros has gone viral, and it has nothing to do with actual tennis.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's to do with a certain look one of the Olympic ball girls gave Djokovic, which has sent social media into somewhat of a frenzy.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999994565769, \"rank\": 5.435245744618622e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's despite the fact that the tennis legend has been married to Jelena Djokovic since 2014.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999994565769, \"rank\": 5.435245744618622e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Find someone that looks at you the same way as this ballgirl looks at Novak Djokovic.pic.twitter.com/njCQe0HrPO  'Females can and will project a powerful beem of support with just their eyes,' tennis fan @mahaprakriti posted on X.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'When Novak turns around [and] sees her\\u2026 he knows to do.'\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Poor thing!'\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@MVPMELSBELLS added.\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'She got caught doing what any of us would do if we got the chance, but now it's frozen in time for everyone to see.'\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ohhh that look in her eyes,' @Juleanne211 said.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I might just look at Nole that same way.'\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@Shakur_Dml, meanwhile, posted: 'So much admiration in her eyes.'\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ooh!'\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@ljmatic123 added.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Now that is a look of\\u2026\\u2026.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"admiration.'\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@RaniAnitaKaur said: 'Yeh that girl got the hots for him.\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was drooling\\u2026'  'She is totally having a crush fan girl moment,' @Raulgunner10 said.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another tennis fan, @Carapan13127382, wrote: 'Love Is in the Air.'\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Andy Murray heartbroken to miss out on 'fairytale ending' at Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:Hollywood megastar set to perform death-defying stunt during Olympics closing ceremony  ArrowMORE:Clare Balding on verge of breaking down while commentating at Olympics  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2532, \"end\": 2543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.407029259849432e-48, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/An